Red Army Resurgent (Time-Life World War II Series)
Time-Life Books | 1979 | ISBN: 0809425203 | English | 216 pages | PDF | 37 MB

This volume overviews the conflict as Russia begins to defeat the Germans. Included is the usual Time-Life collection of hundreds of photographs (many in color), illustrations, and maps that supplement clear and interesting narratives
